# Specflow Instructions

This project is managed by Specflow. The working knowledge you need lives under `.specflow/`:

- `.specflow/workflow.md` — 开发流程阶段、面包屑路由、skill 调度
- `.specflow/spec/` — 按层/领域组织的编码规范（编码前读取受影响领域的 spec）
- `.specflow/changes/` — 活跃与归档变更任务（PRD、执行计划、jsonl 上下文清单）
- `.specflow/workspace/` — 跨会话 journal 与开发者工作记录

Spend time on thinking; you do not need to use the commentary channel to report progress to me.

If a Specflow command is available on your platform (e.g. `/specflow:continue`, `/specflow:finish-work`), prefer it over manual steps.

